AddressInfo.Title: Waco Supercharger
AddressInfo.AccessComments: From I-35N: Take Exit 338A toward US-84/TX-31;  Merge onto N interstate 35 Frontage Rd;  Turn right into the Collin Street Bakery parking lot;  Supercharger will be ahead. / From I-35S: Take Exit 337 toward US-77/Harrison Ave;  Slight right to stay on Harrison Ave; Turn left onto I-35 Srv Rd;  Turn left onto N interstate 35 Frontage Rd; Turn right into the Collin Street Bakery parking lot; Supercharger will be ahead.

GeneralComments: 24 hrs/day. Free to those with unlimited lifetime free supercharging (except for idling fee).
